          "settings": {
            "title": "Wear All Day Comfort",
            "text": "<p>Lightweight, bouncy, and wildly comfortable, Allbirds shoes make any outing feel effortless. Slip in, lace up, or slide them on and enjoy the comfy support.<\/p>",
